.TH record 1 "20 November 1989"
.SH NAME
record - record a sound file from the microphone input
.SH SYNOPSIS
record
.SH DESCRIPTION
Records sound, writing it to stdout in ulaw form, until interrupted.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.nf
SST_RECORD - recording gain, from 0 to 99, default 75
.fi
